### File Operations API

@host = http://localhost:8080
@api = /api/files

### Upload Files
POST {{host}}{{api}}/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="folderPath"

courses/CS101/lectures
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="notes"

Initial upload for CS101
--boundary--

### Get Files by Folder
GET {{host}}{{api}}/folder/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### --- FILE EXPLORER (General) ---

### Get Root Node
GET {{host}}/api/file-explorer/root?academicYearId=1&semesterId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Node by Path
GET {{host}}/api/file-explorer/node?path=some/path
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### --- FILE PREVIEW ---

### Preview File
GET {{host}}/api/file-preview/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
